What you need to know:

Kiguru who is currently the vice chairman of the union, had no opponent therefore he is expected to take over from outgoing chairman Ben Omuodo of Royal Nairobi Golf Club who has been in the union for the past 10 yearsA former captain and chairman of Royal Nairobi, Omuodo will however remain in the council for the next one year as the immediate past chairman which is usually the tradition of the unionBesides the election of new officials, the meeting will also transact among other things, the Chairman and Treasurer's reports, and any other business of which notice would have been circulated under Article 10.5 of the union